    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">===== [ Notification ] =============<br>对于最新版本的Demo版本更新，<br>旧版本的DEMO临时禁用。 <br>=================================</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Demo版本只支持[英语/韩语]语言。  改进的Demo将支持多种语言。</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>&quot;Player &quot;是一条危险的贸易路线，保护运载商人的 Arm 商船穿越 &quot;星天地（交易路）&quot;。  </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>你将与《战斗巨人 RAINBOW 》一起战斗&quot;。</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款复古机械射击游戏，以像素艺术为基础，加入了类似 RPG 的成长要素，是一款在各种装备和盟友的支持下消灭强大敌人的射击 RPG 游戏。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207260/extras/5adf1cb3042ba1f898e261cfe043ed79.poster.avif?t=1765245737\" width=598 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207260/extras/5adf1cb3042ba1f898e261cfe043ed79.webm?t=1765245737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207260/extras/5adf1cb3042ba1f898e261cfe043ed79.mp4?t=1765245737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>俯视图 2D 射击游戏（SH m`Up 类型）SHMUP</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >灵感来自 Technosoft(テクノソフト) 的 90 年代经典射击游戏 &quot;Thunder Force &quot;和 (コンパイル) 的警察射击游戏 &quot;M.U.S.H.A.(Alester)&quot;。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以复古游戏玩法为基础，追求直观的乐趣。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >追踪敌人的匕首、瞬移功能、各种副武器、能量护盾、协助玩家的雇佣兵和同门弟子的尸体、航空母舰大小的武装商船、超乎想象的昆虫怪兽，以及拥有绝对力量的《战斗巨人》！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207260/extras/e76b7432b83ef3399dd0d70f8ee6e72c.poster.avif?t=1765245737\" width=598 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207260/extras/e76b7432b83ef3399dd0d70f8ee6e72c.webm?t=1765245737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207260/extras/e76b7432b83ef3399dd0d70f8ee6e72c.mp4?t=1765245737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>12 （+Alpha）战斗阶段！</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由各种环境战斗方式的战斗阶段组成。 <br>它没有采用比拼子弹数量的子弹风格，而是借鉴了早期射击游戏所追求的瞄准射击等射击游戏元素。射击游戏元素，如早期射击游戏所追求的瞄准射击。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207260/extras/9ed23f3c3783a568c2b97e4bab3621a8.poster.avif?t=1765245737\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207260/extras/9ed23f3c3783a568c2b97e4bab3621a8.webm?t=1765245737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207260/extras/9ed23f3c3783a568c2b97e4bab3621a8.mp4?t=1765245737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>武侠因素、飞剑和特殊技能！！</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据原著故事，在维护游戏中使用武术系统。而不是一味地打出大量弹药出现各种武器，如长矛、斧头和记忆。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207260/extras/c9d07fa3972752d632bd0044d2fa2c14.avif?t=1765245737\" width=620 height=200 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207260/extras/c4b1da97a0ef9a528a59c680791a0a37.avif?t=1765245737\" width=600 height=136 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207260/extras/9130ad025d8f9b22cca2dfc417e3ade0.avif?t=1765245737\" width=660 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>机器人动画风格的美术设计。</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的艺术风格以 90 年代制作原版游戏时具有代表性的巨型机器人动漫风格为基础。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的艺术氛围和机械设计的组织使其与众不同。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每场战斗和中场休息之间都加入了卡通风格的中场休息，以贯穿整个剧情。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207260/extras/e786b3e0c6bad96050e17227c233247c.poster.avif?t=1765245737\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207260/extras/e786b3e0c6bad96050e17227c233247c.webm?t=1765245737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207260/extras/e786b3e0c6bad96050e17227c233247c.mp4?t=1765245737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>升级！, 装备, 技能系统</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过 RPG 元素，您可以获得/交易/五种不同的装备，以适应不同的战斗环境，包括激光、力炮、力剑、力刃、额外燃烧室、力护盾等。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207260/extras/442d3a72fb0bbb526b7236998412e797.avif?t=1765245737\" width=772 height=248 /></span>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207260/extras/e45097566a4675500abc04d774365c8a.avif?t=1765245737\" width=772 height=194 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次对接和战斗都会增加漫画风格的对接,进行整体剧本。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >=============================================</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 将以  启动！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >=============================================</p>",
